A financial information service that makes it easy to identify price differences between exchanges where an arbitrage opportunity might exist.

##History
Service by NYSE-Group.DE was announced on June 27, 2011 (2.1).  [[Bitcoin_Money]] provided a review on June 28, 2011 (2.2).

Another service by mortenh/fnoose was announced on June 10, 2011 (2.3).


